sentences: She has released six albums to date, originally on the German label, Hyperium Records, but in more recent years with the French label Prikosnovénie aka The Fairy World Label.
Love Sessions (2002) with Daemonia Nymphe, Gor, & Lys
Spyros Giasafakis with Christian Wolz (of Daemonia Nymphe) (2004)
Ghost Fish (2005) with Daemonia Nymphe and Nikodemos Triaridis
Stella Maris (2005) with Alquimia & Kerstin Blodig
I Hear the Water Dreaming (2005) with Oöphoi & Mark Krol
Destroying the World to Save It (2005) with IkonJohn-Krol's work has also been included in over a dozen compilations.
